        <h2 class="deck-h reveal d1">Lowest cost. <span class="accent">Vertically integrated.</span> Sovereign by design. First to move.</h2>
        <div class="close-contact reveal d2">
          <a href="mailto:info@navonworld.com">info@navonworld.com</a>
          <a href="https://navon.africa" target="_blank" rel="noopener">navon.africa</a>
        </div>
        <div class="gate-foot reveal d3" style="margin-top:32px">Proprietary &amp; Confidential · H1 2026</div>
